{"id":"1108245518852049345","name":"[Config 2022] UX Writers Need Design Systems, Too!","lastUpdateDate":"2022-05-17T04:12:02.031Z","publisherHandle":"armzies","publisherImage":"https://s3-alpha.figma.com/profile/5f5020ec-7d97-43d5-a719-3fd2c118d867","publisherId":"895220469693603578","publisherName":"Attachai Sawangwong","thumbnailUrl":"https://s3-alpha.figma.com/hub/file/1876946074/36370401-1c96-4dfc-b20c-9ee8fa5bd782-cover.png","description":"<p>UX/UI&nbsp;designers&nbsp;have&nbsp;benefitted&nbsp;from&nbsp;design&nbsp;systems&nbsp;for&nbsp;years,&nbsp;yet&nbsp;no&nbsp;such&nbsp;system&nbsp;exists&nbsp;for&nbsp;UX&nbsp;writers&nbsp;and&nbsp;we&nbsp;wonder&nbsp;why.&nbsp;UX&nbsp;copy&nbsp;is&nbsp;reusable&nbsp;and&nbsp;requires&nbsp;consistency,&nbsp;too.&nbsp;Aren’t&nbsp;we&nbsp;tired&nbsp;of&nbsp;having&nbsp;to&nbsp;edit&nbsp;the&nbsp;same&nbsp;button&nbsp;copy&nbsp;for&nbsp;multiple&nbsp;screens?&nbsp;Aren’t&nbsp;we&nbsp;spending&nbsp;too&nbsp;much&nbsp;time&nbsp;checking&nbsp;copy&nbsp;alignment&nbsp;with&nbsp;our&nbsp;fellow&nbsp;writers?&nbsp;Yes,&nbsp;we&nbsp;are!&nbsp;So&nbsp;we&nbsp;decided&nbsp;to&nbsp;stop&nbsp;the&nbsp;madness and&nbsp;started&nbsp;building&nbsp;our&nbsp;very&nbsp;first&nbsp;copy&nbsp;system&nbsp;right&nbsp;in&nbsp;Figma.</p><p><br></p><p>This&nbsp;needed&nbsp;a&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;workaround&nbsp;and&nbsp;collaboration.&nbsp;It&nbsp;took&nbsp;a&nbsp;team&nbsp;of&nbsp;UX&nbsp;writers&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;UI&nbsp;designer,&nbsp;many&nbsp;discussions&nbsp;over&nbsp;virtual&nbsp;coffee,&nbsp;creativity,&nbsp;and&nbsp;perseverance.&nbsp;We&nbsp;talked&nbsp;about&nbsp;designing&nbsp;an&nbsp;information&nbsp;retrieval&nbsp;system&nbsp;for&nbsp;interface&nbsp;copy,&nbsp;about&nbsp;leveraging&nbsp;Figma’s&nbsp;existing&nbsp;components&nbsp;and&nbsp;variants&nbsp;to&nbsp;support&nbsp;copy&nbsp;search&nbsp;and&nbsp;browse,&nbsp;and&nbsp;about&nbsp;designing&nbsp;a&nbsp;metadata&nbsp;system&nbsp;to&nbsp;support&nbsp;all&nbsp;these.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;end&nbsp;goal?&nbsp;A&nbsp;day&nbsp;when&nbsp;UX&nbsp;writers&nbsp;can&nbsp;finally&nbsp;check&nbsp;for&nbsp;copy&nbsp;consistency&nbsp;quickly.&nbsp;No&nbsp;more&nbsp;asking&nbsp;around,&nbsp;no&nbsp;more&nbsp;opening&nbsp;3&nbsp;different&nbsp;files&nbsp;to&nbsp;look&nbsp;for&nbsp;a&nbsp;copy&nbsp;string.&nbsp;Just&nbsp;pure&nbsp;efficiency&nbsp;and&nbsp;more&nbsp;time&nbsp;to&nbsp;do&nbsp;high-value&nbsp;UX&nbsp;writing&nbsp;work.</p>","url":"https://www.figma.com/community/file/1108245518852049345"}
